FestivalPlanner.Agenda

Class Show

  • java.lang.Object
    • FestivalPlanner.Agenda.Show
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Show
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Contains information about a show, such as the time, name, artist and podium.

    Show is used by Agenda to collect all shows.

    See Also:
    Agenda.getShows(), Serialized Form

      • Show

        public Show()
        Constructor containing no parameters, used by the ShowEditorGUI.

        This constructor sets:

        • This name to "New Show".
        • This startTime to "00:00".
        • This endTime to "23:00".
        • This expectedPopularity to 50.
        • This podium to null.
        • This artists to null.
